      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. How does the city typically handle these kinds of boundary disputes when they're discovered mid-construction? Is there a formal process for resolving an encroachment if the developer claims it was a minor measurement error, or is it treated as a more serious violation of the lot lines?",
